[[Socket Address]] is the way to identify a [[Network Socket]] to other [[Hosts|Host]].

It consists of:

* The [[Transport Protocol|Transport Layer]] used ([[TCP|Transmission Control Protocol]] or [[UDP|User Datagram Protocol]])
* [[IP Address]]
* [[Port Number|Port (Networking)]]